{"title": "The MintFace Mintpass Origin Story", "slug": "the-mintface-mintpass-origin-story", "date": "2022-04-24", "author": "theline1", "excerpt": "", "categories": ["MintFace News", "pfp", "wen mint"], "featuredImage": "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/set1.png", "images": ["https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2022/04/second2kdetail.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2022/04/Screen-Shot-2022-04-24-at-11.40.23-AM-1.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2022/04/first2kdetail.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2022/04/second2kdetail.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2022/04/second2kdetail.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2022/04/Screen-Shot-2022-04-24-at-11.40.23-AM-1.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2022/04/first2kdetail.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2022/04/Screen-Shot-2022-04-24-at-11.40.23-AM-1.png", "https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2022/04/first2kdetail.png"], "content": "<p>6 months ago I said something dumb.</p><p>dumb.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Experiment. <br />1/1 art &gt; 10,000 project <br /><br />Follow <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mintfaced</a> and you’re in. <br /><br />On reaching 10,000 fans…<br /><br />A huge 1/1 NFT artwork featuring the first 10,000 MintFace fans will be minted and made available. <br /><br />RT to make it so.</p>&mdash; MintFace.eth 🍒 (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1447006895055593472?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 10, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>Why is it dumb? It is a promise with no idea how to deliver. That creates a risk of breaking the promise. Rugs are stitched together on a sea of broken promises.</p><p>I was reminded by one of the MintFace community recently who remembered the tweet so put out a call for halp.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Way back in August I said that a 10k collage of followers would be minted at 10k. <br /><br />Now I hope no one remembers. No idea how to create it!</p>&mdash; MintFace.eth 🍒 (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1516578042990456832?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 20, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>Fortunately, one of the NFT Digital Artist Economy alumni came to the rescue.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Ah. I misread ingesting as interesting. I’m here for the interesting Jpegs from twitters api.</p>&mdash; Matthew Hirschey💡 (@matthewhirschey) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/matthewhirschey/status/1516582597157171201?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 20, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>Matthew Hirschey is a giga-science brain from Duke University and began coding up a way to get all us MintFaces together in a JPEG.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@matthewhirschey\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2022/04/Screen-Shot-2022-04-24-at-11.40.23-AM-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1418\" height=\"1110\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2022/04/Screen-Shot-2022-04-24-at-11.40.23-AM-1.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2022/04/Screen-Shot-2022-04-24-at-11.40.23-AM-1.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2022/04/Screen-Shot-2022-04-24-at-11.40.23-AM-1.png 1418w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@matthewhirschey\">Matthew Hirschey's first two collections on Foundation</a></figcaption></figure><h3 id=\"why-mintfaces\">Why MintFaces</h3><p>From the beginning of NFT Twitter culture, the process of minting has been central to our community. It is what we do or decide not to do. \"Are we minting this?\" We ask each other 'wen mint' and then get to decide to be part of the project 'for the culture' ...or not.</p><p>Getting 'mintfaced' is something we have all experienced... when you just can't stop minting your favorite kind of art.</p><p><em><em>For Adam McBride, it is historical NFTs. The collection is almost endless.</em></em><br /><em><em>For Punk6529, it is generative art. So much ArtBlocks.</em></em><br /><em><em>For BatSoupYum, it is CryptoDickButts. Enuff said.</em></em><br /><em><em>For MintFace it has turned out to be mostly rugs. 😂 def NFA.</em></em></p><p>Over the last year, MintFace has met many new NFT frens through Twitter and is truly grateful for the world and opportunities this has opened up.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2022/04/first2kdetail.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1199\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2022/04/first2kdetail.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2022/04/first2kdetail.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2022/04/first2kdetail.png 1199w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h3 id=\"mintface-mintpass\">MintFace MintPass</h3><p>The MintFace Mintpass celebrates all of us getting mintfaced each and every day.</p><p>In 1/1 szn, in photography szn and in NFTs are ded szn. You have all been here, almost every day.</p><h3 id=\"mintface-mintpass-utility\">MintFace MintPass Utility</h3><p>There is utility. You get access to virtual places and spaces that will not otherwise be available.</p><p>You have heard of art without utility. <strong><strong>This NFT is utility without the art.</strong></strong></p><p>You don't get the art. That is right. The art will be sold separately, like the AA batteries in your favorite 80's action figure.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2022/04/second2kdetail.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1199\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w600/2022/04/second2kdetail.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/size/w1000/2022/04/second2kdetail.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/content/images/2022/04/second2kdetail.png 1199w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h3 id=\"mintface-mintpass-price\">MintFace MintPass Price</h3><p>It would seem silly to mint and sell your own pfp back to you (although we have seen sillier ideas in NFTs. RIP Kevin). We will not do that.</p><p>Instead, the MintFace MintPass will be free + gas. ⛽️.</p><p>Whatt.</p><p>Yes, you can decide whether it has utility worth paying for.</p><p>...and please, remember, do not buy it for the art. The art will be sold separately.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Get your face minted in the MintFace 10k poster…<br /><br />…and receive a 100 pixel square in the 10,000 pixel art!  <br /><br />9,473 secured (shown below).<br />527 spots left.  <br /><br />gotta be following <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mintfaced</a> to make it count. <a href=\"https://t.co/7NXhZ7I5RC\">pic.twitter.com/7NXhZ7I5RC</a></p>&mdash; MintFace.eth 🍒 (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1517806609707134976?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 23, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><h3 id=\"wen-mint\">Wen Mint</h3><p>Not yet. We are not ready.</p><p>There are 502 more MintFaces to find until there are 10,000 upstanding NFT Twitter community members following <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced\">@mintfaced</a>.</p><p><strong><strong>Remember this is not art, it is 100% pure utility.</strong></strong></p><p><em><em>Kind of like having your face on your drivers licence. You get to go places fast ;)</em></em></p><p>RT and tell your frens to follow <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced\">@mintfaced</a> and the rest will unfold.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Ok not sure people understand what is going on here. <br /><br />MintFace is launching a MintFace Pass.<br /><br />The art is many NFT Twitter faces. <br /><br />…and is minted to create the pass. <br /><br />Your face + mint = MintFace Pass. 👀🍒 <a href=\"https://t.co/vYrEpqDSUT\">pic.twitter.com/vYrEpqDSUT</a></p>&mdash; MintFace.eth 🍒 (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1517968475607556096?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 23, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure>"}